01:15:08.670 --> 01:15:12.007
So listen to me.
Front line. you're the first ones out.

1394
01:15:12.090 --> 01:15:14.676
If you're not perfect.
everything else is a disaster.

1395
01:15:15.177 --> 01:15:18.138
You have to be what? Perfect.

1396
01:15:18.222 --> 01:15:22.059
[female singer]
♪ Underneath the Christmas tree ♪

1397
01:15:22.142 --> 01:15:25.145
[male singer]
♪ I just want you for my own ♪

1398
01:15:25.938 --> 01:15:30.400
[female singer]
♪ More than you can ever know ♪

1399
01:15:30.484 --> 01:15:36.782
♪ Make my wish come true ♪

