01:15:58.136 --> 01:16:00.847
Two. two. three. four. five. six. seven.

1406
01:16:00.931 --> 01:16:01.765
and one.

1407
01:16:02.933 --> 01:16:03.976
Five. good!

1408
01:16:04.059 --> 01:16:07.646
And one. two. three. four.
five. six. seven. eight.

1409
01:16:07.729 --> 01:16:08.689
Two. two. three…

1410
01:16:08.772 --> 01:16:11.817
[Jalyn] In ten years.
I wanna be at the Royal Ballet.

1411
01:16:11.900 --> 01:16:15.571
It's my dream to go there
and be able to dance on their stage. so…

1412
01:16:15.654 --> 01:16:17.155
[Debbie] Five. six. seven. eight.

1413
01:16:17.239 --> 01:16:19.283
One. two. three. four. five!

1414
01:16:20.284 --> 01:16:21.159
Go!

1415
01:16:23.370 --> 01:16:26.039
I wanna go to Stanford
and double major in kinesiology and dance.

1416
01:16:26.123 --> 01:16:27.165
Ooh. look at you! [laughs]

1417
01:16:27.249 --> 01:16:29.668
[Debbie] Two. three. four. five. go.

1418
01:16:29.751 --> 01:16:32.838
[Cathie] One. two. three.
four. five. six. seven. eight.

1419
01:16:32.921 --> 01:16:34.840
[female student 1]
Hopefully. I'll become somebody

1420
01:16:34.923 --> 01:16:38.510
that changes the world. honestly.
'cause I-- I wanna see that happen.

1421
01:16:39.261 --> 01:16:42.931
[Cathie] One. two. three.
four. five. six. seven and one.

1422
01:16:43.640 --> 01:16:45.434
And five. six. seven…

1423
01:16:45.517 --> 01:16:47.144
I wanna be. like. a well-known dancer.

1424
01:16:47.227 --> 01:16:49.646
Maybe a choreographer.
but I love to dance.

1425
01:16:49.730 --> 01:16:51.773
Like. it's my passion.

